{"id": "art-2782", "label": "Art. 2782", "title": "Art. 2782", "slug": "art-2782", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_828942638\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1041\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_828942638\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 278<sup>2</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1543497004\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1040\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1543497004\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În cazul\nraporturilor juridice de munc&#259; neîntemeiate pe un contract individual de\nmunc&#259;, prin legi speciale pot fi reglementate modele de organizare a\nmuncii numai cu respectarea urm&#259;toarelor condi&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_379728938\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1039\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_379728938\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>angajatorul\ninformeaz&#259; persoana care î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activitatea în\ncadrul respectivului raport de munc&#259; cu privire la:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_355573710\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1038\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_355573710\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(i)faptul c&#259; programul de lucru este variabil,\nnum&#259;rul de ore garantate în plat&#259; &#351;i remunera&#355;ia pentru\nmunca prestat&#259; în plus fa&#355;&#259; de orele garantate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1729306805\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1037\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1729306805\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(ii)orele &#351;i zilele de referin&#355;&#259; în care\npersoanei i se poate cere s&#259; lucreze;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1688160282\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1036\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1688160282\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(iii)perioada minim&#259; de în&#351;tiin&#355;are\nprealabil&#259; la care are dreptul persoana înainte de începerea unei sarcini\nde serviciu &#351;i, dup&#259; caz, termenul-limit&#259; de anulare a acesteia;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1096380119\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1035\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1096380119\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>angajatorul\nsolicit&#259; persoanei care î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activitatea în\ncadrul respectivului raport de munc&#259; s&#259; presteze munca doar dac&#259;\nsunt îndeplinite cumulativ urm&#259;toarele condi&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1342380898\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1034\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1342380898\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(i)munca este prestat&#259; în cadrul orelor &#351;i\nzilelor de referin&#355;&#259; prestabilite, comunicate persoanei conform\nprevederilor lit. a) pct. (ii);</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_63332368\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1033\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_63332368\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(ii)persoana este informat&#259; de angajatorul s&#259;u în\nprivin&#355;a unei sarcini de serviciu cu respectarea perioadei rezonabile de\nîn&#351;tiin&#355;are prealabil&#259;, conform prevederilor lit. a) pct. (iii).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_863524289\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1032\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_863524289\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Informarea persoanei men&#355;ionat&#259; la alin. (1)\nlit. a) se realizeaz&#259; în condi&#355;iile stabilite la art. 278<sup>1</sup>\nalin. (3), într-o perioad&#259; de cel mult 7 zile lucr&#259;toare de la data\nprimei zile de munc&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1327703241\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1031\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1327703241\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Pot face excep&#355;ie de la prevederile alin. (1) lit.\nb) raporturile de munc&#259; sau de serviciu desf&#259;&#351;urate de\npersonalul din cadrul serviciilor publice de urgen&#355;&#259;, personalul din\ncadrul sistemului de ap&#259;rare, ordine public&#259; &#351;i securitate\nna&#355;ional&#259;, personalul diplomatic &#351;i consular, magistra&#355;i,\npersonalul auxiliar de specialitate al instan&#355;elor judec&#259;tore&#351;ti\n&#351;i al parchetelor de pe lâng&#259; acestea, respectiv raporturile de\nserviciu ale func&#355;ionarilor publici.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}